    <title>线性方程组解的基础概念与性质</title>
    
  
        <exercises xml:id="exercises-la4_1">
            <title>练习题</title>              
            <!-- Q1 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        齐次线性方程  <m>  \left\{\begin{array}{l}x_{1}+2 x_{2}+3 x_{3}+2 x_{4}+5 x_{5}=0 \\ 2 x_{1}+2 x_{2}+x_{3}+3 x_{4}+x_{5}=0 \\ 3 x_{1}+4 x_{2}+3 x_{3}+4 x_{4}+3 x_{5}=0\end{array}\right.  </m>  的基础解系是_____

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        解：<m>  \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\begin{array}{lllll}1  &amp;  2  &amp;  3  &amp;  2  &amp;  5 \\ 2  &amp;  2  &amp;  1  &amp;  3  &amp;  1 \\ 3  &amp;  4  &amp;  3  &amp;  4  &amp;  3\end{array}\right)\xrightarrow[ r_{3}-3r_{1}]{r_{2}-2r_{1}}\left(\begin{array}{ccccc}1  &amp;  2  &amp;  3  &amp;  2  &amp;  5 \\ 0  &amp;  -2  &amp;  -5  &amp;  -1  &amp;  -9 \\ 0  &amp;  -2  &amp;  -6  &amp;  -2  &amp;  -12\end{array}\right)\xrightarrow[ r_{3}-r_{2}]{\begin{array}{l}-r_{2} \\ -r_{3}\end{array}}\\ \left(\begin{array}{lllll}1  &amp;  2  &amp;  3  &amp;  2  &amp;  5 \\ 0  &amp;  2  &amp;  5  &amp;  1  &amp;  9 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  1  &amp;  3\end{array}\right)\xrightarrow[ r_{1}-3r_{3}]{r_{2}-5r_{3}} \left(\begin{array}{ccccc}1  &amp;  2  &amp;  0  &amp;  -1  &amp;  -4 \\ 0  &amp;  2  &amp;  0  &amp;  -4  &amp;  -6 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  1  &amp;  3\end{array}\right)\xrightarrow[ \frac 12r_{2}]{r_{1}-r_2}  \left(\begin{array}{ccccc}1  &amp;  0  &amp;  0  &amp;  3  &amp;  2 \\ 0  &amp;  1  &amp;  0  &amp;  -2  &amp;  -3 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  1  &amp;  3\end{array}\right) </m>  ,同解方程组  <m>  \left\{\begin{array}{l}x_{1}=-3 x_{4}-2 x_{5} \\ x_{2}=2 x_{4}+3 x_{5} \\ x_{3}=-x_{4}-3 x_{5}\end{array}\right.  </m> , </p> 

                    <p> 令<m>\begin{array}{l}
                    \left(\begin{array}{l}
                    x_{4} \\
                    x_{5}
                    \end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{l}
                    1 \\
                    0
                    \end{array}\right),\left(\begin{array}{l}
                    0 \\
                    1
                    \end{array}\right)
                    \end{array}</m> </p> 

                    <p> 则基础解系是  <m> \boldsymbol{\eta}_{1}=(-3,2,-1,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}}, \boldsymbol{\eta}_{2}=(-2,3,-3,0,1)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>
                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>

            <!-- Q2 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        解方程组  <m> \left\{\begin{array}{ll}6 x_{1}-2 x_{2}+2 x_{3}+x_{4} &amp; =3, \\ x_{1}-x_{2}  +x_{4} &amp; =1, \\ 2 x_{1}  +x_{3}+3 x_{4} &amp; =2 .\end{array}\right. </m> 

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        <m>\overline{\boldsymbol{A}}=\left(\begin{array}{cccc:c}6  &amp;  -2  &amp;  2  &amp;  1  &amp;  3 \\ 1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  1 \\ 2  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  3  &amp;  2\end{array}\right) \rightarrow\left(\begin{array}{cccc:c}1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  1 \\ 2  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  3  &amp;   2 \\ 6  &amp;  -2  &amp;  2  &amp;  1  &amp;   3\end{array}\right) \xrightarrow[r_{3}-6r_1]{r_{2}-2 r_{1}}\left(\begin{array}{cccc:c}1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp; 1 \\ 0  &amp;  2  &amp;  1  &amp;  1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  4  &amp;  2  &amp;  -5  &amp;  -3\end{array}\right)\xrightarrow[]{r_{3}-2 r_{2}} \left(\begin{array}{cccc:c}1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  1 \\ 0  &amp;  2  &amp;  1  &amp;  1  &amp;  0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0  &amp;  -7  &amp;  -3\end{array}\right)\xrightarrow[\begin{array}{l}r_2-r_3\\r_1-r_3
                            \end{array}]{-\frac 17r_{3}} \left(\begin{array}{cccc:c}1  &amp;  -1  &amp;  0  &amp;  0  &amp;  \frac 47 \\ 0  &amp;  2  &amp;  1  &amp;  0  &amp;  -\frac 37 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  \frac 37\end{array}\right)   </m> , 同解方程组  <m> \left\{\begin{array}{l}x_{1}=\frac{4}{7}+x_{2}, \\ x_{3}=-\frac{3}{7}-2 x_{2}, \\ x_{4}=\frac{3}{7}\end{array}\right. </m> </p> 

                            <p> 非齐次方程通解为  <m> k[1,1,-2,0]^{\mathrm{T}}+\left[\frac{4}{7}, 0,-\frac{3}{7}, \frac{3}{7}\right]^{\mathrm{T}}, k \in \mathrm{R} </m>
                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>

            <!-- Q3 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        已知  <m> \boldsymbol{\beta}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\beta}_{2} </m>  是非齐次线性方程组  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=\boldsymbol{b} </m>  的两个不同的解,  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2} </m>  是对应齐次线性方程组  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的基础解系,  <m> k_{1}, k_{2} </m>  为任意常数,则方程组  <m> A x=b </m>  的通解是 ( ) 

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <choices>
                    <choice>
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> k_{1}\alpha_{1}+k_{2}\left(\alpha_{1}+\alpha_{2}\right)+\frac{\beta_{1}-\beta_{2}}{2} </m>
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
                    
                    <choice correct="yes">
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> k_{1} \alpha_{1}+k_{2}\left(\alpha_{1}-\alpha_{2}\right)+\frac{\beta_{1}+\beta_{2}}{2} </m>
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
    
                    <choice>
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> k_{1} \alpha_{1}+k_{2}\left(\beta_{1}+\beta_{2}\right)+\frac{\beta_{1}-\beta_{2}}{2} </m>
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
    
                    <choice>
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> k_{1} \alpha_{1}+k_{2}\left(\beta_{1}-\beta_{2}\right)+\frac{\beta_{1}+\boldsymbol{\beta}_{2}}{2} </m>
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
                
                </choices>
                
                <answer>
                        <p>
                            解: 因为  <m> \beta_{1}, \beta_{2} </m>  是  <m> A x=b </m>  的两个不同的解,
                            所以  <m> \frac{\beta_{1}+\beta_{2}}{2} </m>  是  <m> A x=b </m>  的一个解, 而  <m> \frac{\beta_{1}-\beta_{2}}{2} </m>  是  <m> A x=0 </m>  的一个解.因为  <m> \alpha_{1}, \alpha_{2} </m>  是  <m> A x=0 </m>  的基础解系,
                            所以  <m> \alpha_{1}, \alpha_{1}+\alpha_{2} </m>  以及  <m> \alpha_{1}, \alpha_{1}-\alpha_{2} </m>  都可成为的基础解系（均线性无关）,故选(B) 
                        </p>
                  </answer>
            </exercise>
    

            <!-- Q4 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        设  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3} </m>  是四元非齐次线性方程组  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=\boldsymbol{\beta} </m>  的三个解向量,秩  <m>  r(\boldsymbol{A})=3, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}=(1,2,3,4)^{\mathrm{T}}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}=(0,1,2,3)^{\mathrm{T}}, k  </m>  为任意常数,则方程组  <m>  \boldsymbol{A x}=\boldsymbol{\beta}  </m>  的通解是 ( ) 

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <choices>
                    <choice>
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                 <m> (1,2,3,4)^{\mathrm{T}}+k(1,1,1,1)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
                    
                    <choice>
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> (1,2,3,4)^{\mathrm{T}}+k(0,1,2,3)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
    
                    <choice correct="yes">
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> (1,2,3,4)^{\mathrm{T}}+k(2,3,4,5)^{\mathrm{T}} </m> 
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
    
                    <choice>
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> (1,2,3,4)^{\mathrm{T}}+k(3,4,5,6)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
                
                </choices>
                
                <answer>
                        <p>
                            解: 秩  <m> r(\boldsymbol{A})=3 \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{A X}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的基础解系中含有  <m> n-r(\boldsymbol{A})=4-3=1 </m>  个向量. </p> 

                            <p>  <m> \boldsymbol{A \alpha}_{1}=\boldsymbol{\beta}, \quad \boldsymbol{A}\left(\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}\right)=2 \boldsymbol{\beta} \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{A}\left(\left(\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}\right)-2 \alpha_{1}\right)=0 </m> 
                           所以  <m> \left(\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}\right)-2 \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}=(0,1,2,3)^{\mathrm{T}}-2(1,2,3,4)^{\mathrm{T}}=-(2,3,4,5)^{\mathrm{T}} </m> 为  <m> \boldsymbol{A X}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的一个非零解. </p> 
                           
                            <p> 所以  <m> (1,2,3,4)^{\mathrm{T}}+k(2,3,4,5)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  为方程组  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=\boldsymbol{\beta} </m>  的通解, 故选 (C) 
                        </p>
                  </answer>
            </exercise>
    

            <!-- Q5 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        设  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\alpha_{1}, \alpha_{2}, \alpha_{3}\right) </m>  为3阶矩阵. 若  <m> \alpha_{1}, \alpha_{2}  </m>  线性无关,且  <m>  \alpha_{3}=-\alpha_{1}+2 \alpha_{2}  </m> , 则线性方程组  <m>  A x=0  </m>  的通解为 ______

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        解: 由  <m> \alpha_{1}, \alpha_{2}  </m>  线性无关可得  <m> r(\boldsymbol{A}) \geq 2 </m> . 由  <m> \alpha_{3}=-\alpha_{1}+2 \alpha_{2} </m>  可得  <m> -\alpha_{1}+2 \alpha_{2}-\alpha_{3}=0 </m> , 从而  <m> \alpha_{1}, \alpha_{2}, \alpha_{3} </m>  线性相关, 于是  <m> r(\boldsymbol{A}) \leq 2 </m> , 因此  <m> r(\boldsymbol{A})=2  </m> .所以  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=0  </m>  的基础解系中所含解向量个数为  <m>  3-r(A)=3-2=1 </m> . 又因为  <m> -\alpha_{1}+2 \alpha_{2}-\alpha_{3}=0 </m>  可写为  <m> \left(\alpha_{1}, \alpha_{2}, \alpha_{3}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}-1 \\ 2 \\ -1\end{array}\right)=0 </m> 
                        所以  <m> (-1,2,-1)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  是  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的一个解, 即方程的基础解系.则线性方程组  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的通解为  <m> k(-1,2,-1)^{\mathrm{T}}(k \in \mathbf{R}) </m> . 

                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>

            <!-- Q6 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        已知  <m> 4 </m>  阶方阵  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}\right), \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4} </m>  均为 <m> 4 </m>  维列向量, 其中  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4} </m>  线性无关,  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}=2 \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}-\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}  </m> . 如果  <m> \boldsymbol{\beta}=\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4} </m> ,求线性方程组  <m>  \boldsymbol{A x}=\boldsymbol{\beta} </m>  的通解. 

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <answer>
                    <p>
                        法1: 因为  <m> \boldsymbol{\beta}=\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}, \Rightarrow  </m>   <m>  \left(\begin{array}{llll}\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1},  &amp;  \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2},  &amp;  \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3},  &amp;  \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{l}1 \\ 1 \\ 1 \\ 1\end{array}\right)=\boldsymbol{\beta}  </m>  </p> 

                        <p>  <m> \Rightarrow(1,1,1,1)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  为的一个特解  <m> \boldsymbol{A} \boldsymbol{X}=\boldsymbol{\beta} </m>  </p> 

                        <p> 因为  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4} </m>  线性无关，且  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}=2 \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}-\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3} </m>  知  <m> r(\boldsymbol{A})=3  </m> 
                        <m>  \boldsymbol{A} \boldsymbol{X}=\mathbf{0} </m>  基础解系中含有  <m> 4-r(\boldsymbol{A})=4-3=1 </m>  个解向量. 又  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}=2 \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}-\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3} \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}-2 \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}=\mathbf{0} \Rightarrow\left(\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}1 \\ -2 \\ 1 \\ 0\end{array}\right)=\mathbf{0} </m> . 即基础解为 <m> (1,-2,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  </p> 

                        <p>  <m> \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{A x}=\boldsymbol{\beta} </m>  的通解为  <m> (1,1,1,1)^{\mathrm{T}}+k(1,-2,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}}(k \in \mathbf{R}) </m> . </p> 

                        <p> 法2: 令  <m> \boldsymbol{A} \boldsymbol{x}=\boldsymbol{\beta} </m>  的解为  <m> \boldsymbol{x}=\left(x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}, x_{4}\right)^{\mathrm{T}} </m> .
                        得  <m> x_{1} \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}+x_{2} \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+x_{3} \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}+x_{4} \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}=\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4} </m> . 将  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}=2 \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}-\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3} </m>  代入得
                        <me> 
                        \begin{array}{l}
                        x_{1}\left(2 \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}-\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}\right)+x_{2} \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+x_{3} \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}+x_{4} \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}=2 \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}-\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4} . \\
                        \left(2 x_{1}+x_{2}-3\right) \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}+\left(-x_{1}+x_{3}\right) \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}+\left(x_{4}-1\right) \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}=\mathbf{0} .
                        \end{array}
                        </me>  </p> 

                        <p> 因为  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4} </m>  线性无关, 知  <m> \left\{\begin{array}{l}2 x_{1}+x_{2}-3=0, \\ -x_{1}+x_{3}=0, \\ x_{4}-1=0,\end{array}\right. </m>  </p> 

                        <p>  <m> \overline{\boldsymbol{A}}=\left(\begin{array}{cccc:c}2  &amp;  1  &amp;  0  &amp;  0  &amp;  3 \\ -1  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  0  &amp; 0 \\ 0  &amp;  0  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  1\end{array}\right) \Rightarrow\left\{\begin{array}{l}x_{2}=3-2 x \\ x_{3}=x_{1} \\ x_{4}=1\end{array}\right. </m>  </p> 

                        <p>  <m> \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{A x}=\boldsymbol{\beta} </m>  的通解为  <m> \left(\begin{array}{l}0 \\ 3 \\ 0 \\ 1\end{array}\right)+k\left(\begin{array}{c}1 \\ -2 \\ 1 \\ 0\end{array}\right)(k \in \mathbf{R}) </m> 
                    </p>
                </answer>
            </exercise>

            <!-- Q7 -->
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p>
                        设  <m> \boldsymbol{A}=\left(\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}\right) </m>  是  <m> 4 </m>  阶矩阵,  <m> \boldsymbol{A}^{*} </m>  为  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的伴随矩阵, 若  <m>  (1,0,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  是  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=0 </m>  的一个基础解系，则  <m> \boldsymbol{A}^{*} \boldsymbol{x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的基础解系可为（）

                    </p>
                </statement>
                <choices>
                    <choice>
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3} </m> 
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
                    
                    <choice>
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2} </m> 
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
    
                    <choice>
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3} </m>
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
    
                    <choice correct="yes">
                        <statement>
                            <p>
                                <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4} </m> 
                            </p>
                        </statement>
                    </choice>
                
                </choices>
                
                <answer>
                        <p>
                            【分析】:(1)由  <m> r(\boldsymbol{A}) \Rightarrow r\left(\boldsymbol{A}^{*}\right)= </m>  ?(2)  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的列向量为  <m> \boldsymbol{A}^{*} \boldsymbol{X}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的解 </p> 

                            <p> 解: 因为  <m> (1,0,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  是  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的一个基础解系  <m> \Rightarrow n-r(\boldsymbol{A})=4-r(\boldsymbol{A})=1 </m> 
                            <me> 
                           \begin{array}{l}
                           \Rightarrow r(\boldsymbol{A})=3, \text { 且 }|\boldsymbol{A}|=0 \\
                           \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{A}^{*} \boldsymbol{A}=|\boldsymbol{E}| \boldsymbol{E}=\boldsymbol{O} \\
                           \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{A}^{*}\left(\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}\right)=\boldsymbol{O}
                           \end{array}
                            </me>  </p> 
                           
                            <p> 即  <m> \boldsymbol{A} </m>  的列向量为  <m> \boldsymbol{A}^{*} \boldsymbol{X}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的解.又因为
                            <me> 
                            r\left(\boldsymbol{A}^{*}\right)=\left\{\begin{array}{l}
                           n, r(\boldsymbol{A})=n \\
                           1, r(\boldsymbol{A})=n-1 \\
                           0, r(\boldsymbol{A}) \lt n-1
                           \end{array} \Rightarrow r\left(\boldsymbol{A}^{*}\right)=1\right.
                            </me>  </p> 
                           
                            <p> 所以  <m> \boldsymbol{A}^{*} \boldsymbol{x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的基础解系由三个线性无关的解向量组成, 排除  <m> \mathrm{A}, \mathrm{B} </m> .  <m> (1,0,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}} </m>  是  <m> \boldsymbol{A x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的一个基础解系  <m> \Rightarrow\left(\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4}\right)(1,0,1,0)^{\mathrm{T}}=\mathbf{0} </m>   <m> \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}+\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}=0 \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}=-\boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3} </m> , 即  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}  </m>  线性相关  <m>  \Rightarrow \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{1}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3} </m>  线性相关故  <m> \boldsymbol{A}^{*} \boldsymbol{x}=\mathbf{0} </m>  的基础解系可为  <m> \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{2}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{3}, \boldsymbol{\alpha}_{4} </m> , 故选(D)

                        </p>
                  </answer>
            </exercise>
    

        </exercises>
